title: For Sale:  Just Right Carbine 9mm
postcontent:
Well, as much as I love my carbine, I need to sell it in favor of some other priorities. For sale is a 9mm Just Right carbine. The rifle comes with the JR disassembly/assembly tool and a mid-quality reflex sight.

For those unfamiliar with JR carbines, they can be set up to fire 9mm, .40 S&W and .45 ACP, and are blowback operated. They use Glock magazines, two of which come with the weapon. The collapsible stock, handle, and trigger group are all AR-15 sourced, leaving you with some easy-to find parts. The gun can be set up in about 2 minutes for either right or left handed fire.

I love the thing, but I have to make some hard choices about what to keep and sell.

VA residents only (unless you're doing an FFL transfer), and I prefer to deal with a CCW holder or LEO. Being able to use your pistol carry ammo in a more powerful, more accurate package is really handy -- my glock magazines interchange with my pistol, which is nice.
